						 <p>I can't wait to defeat a snot monster and cure my allergies once and for all. +1</p> <p>Questions that don't have to be answered but I'm curious:</p> <p>1) Does each instance of SCP-3753-A have the same physical strength and fighting acumen as the subject? Like if Mike Tyson used 3753, would his -A be a talented boxer and a hard hitter?</p> <p>2) Does the type of ailment change the strength of the -A? Would a cancer based -A would be tougher to beat than a common cold based -A?</p> 
